---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms & Conditions | Uddin Investment Ltd">
  
    <!-- Terms Content -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="mb-12 border-b border-slate-100 pb-8 text-center md:text-left">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4 italic">Terms & <span class="text-blue-600">Conditions</span></h1>
        <p class="text-slate-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm italic">Last Updated: March 2026</p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-10 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed italic font-medium">
        
        <!-- Section 1 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 underline decoration-blue-500 underline-offset-8 italic">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p>
            Welcome to Uddin Investment Ltd ("Company", "we", "us", "our"). These Terms & Conditions govern your use of our website and our professional property services, including our Guaranteed Rent scheme and Portfolio Management. By engaging with our services, you agree to comply with these terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 2 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 underline decoration-blue-500 underline-offset-8 italic">2. Professional Services</h2>
          <p>
            Uddin Investment Ltd provides property management services specialized in London and Essex. Our primary service is the Guaranteed Rent scheme, where we enter into a contractual agreement with landlords to provide a fixed monthly income.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4">
            Specific terms regarding rent amounts, duration (1-5 years), and maintenance responsibilities will be detailed in the individual Management Agreement signed by both parties.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 3 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 underline decoration-blue-500 underline-offset-8 italic">3. Landlord Responsibilities</h2>
          <p>To qualify for our services, Landlords must ensure:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-4">
            <li>The property is in a habitable and safe condition.</li>
            <li>All mandatory safety certificates (Gas Safety, EICR, EPC) are valid and up to date.</li>
            <li>Proof of ownership and appropriate insurance are provided upon request.</li>
            <li>Any existing mortgages allow for the property to be let via a corporate or management agreement.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 4 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 underline decoration-blue-500 underline-offset-8 italic">4. Guaranteed Rent Scheme</h2>
          <p>
            Our Guaranteed Rent offer is subject to property inspection and local authority requirements. While we aim to provide 0% commission management, certain structural repairs remain the responsibility of the Landlord unless otherwise stated in the specific Management Agreement.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 5 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 underline decoration-blue-500 underline-offset-8 italic">5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            Uddin Investment Ltd will perform its duties with professional care and skill. However, we are not liable for any indirect or consequential losses, including structural damage to the property caused by third parties or environmental factors beyond our reasonable control.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 6 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 underline decoration-blue-500 underline-offset-8 italic">6. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>
            These Terms & Conditions are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of England and Wales. Any disputes arising from these terms shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of England and Wales.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 7 -->
        <section class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 italic underline decoration-blue-600 underline-offset-4">Contact Information</h2>
          <p class="text-sm">For any legal inquiries regarding these terms, please contact us at:</p>
          <div class="mt-4 text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 italic">
            <p>Uddin Investment Ltd</p>
            <p>5 Elm Lawn Close, Uxbridge, UB8 1NX</p>
            <p>Email: info@uddininvestmentltd.com</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-blue-600">Company Number: 16787880</p>
          </div>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  

</Layout>

<style>
  /* Custom prose-like spacing */
  h2 { margin-top: 2rem; }
  p { margin-top: 1rem; }
</style>